'''艾莉森·琳恩·里德'''（{{lang-en|Allison Lynn Reed}}，{{bd|1994年|6月8日||}}）生于美国密歇根州卡拉马祖，是一名曾先后代表格鲁吉亚、以色列和立陶宛参加比赛的女子花样滑冰运动员，主攻冰舞<ref name=ISU-1920>{{cite web |url= http://www.isuresults.com/bios/isufs00103181.htm |title= Allison REED / Saulius AMBRULEVICIUS: 2019/2020 |publisher= International Skating Union |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200421170741/http://www.isuresults.com/bios/isufs00103181.htm |archivedate= 2020-04-21 |deadurl= unfit }}</ref>。她的母亲是日本人，父亲是美国人<ref name=NJ100223>{{cite news |url= http://www.nj.com/olympics/index.ssf/2010/02/zaretsky_reed_siblings_make_je.html |title= Zaretsky, Reed siblings make Jersey proud in Olympic ice dancing |first= Dave |last= D'Alessandro |work= The Star-Ledger |date=2010-02-23 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120430200216/http://www.nj.com/olympics/index.ssf/2010/02/zaretsky_reed_siblings_make_je.html |archivedate= 2012-04-30 |deadurl= yes |access-date= 2011-06-09 }}</ref>。她的姐姐[[凯茜·里德|凯茜]]和哥哥[[克里斯·里德|克里斯]]都是花样滑冰冰舞选手<ref name=NJ100223/>。三兄弟姐妹在新泽西州沃伦镇区长大<ref name=TW140206>{{cite news |url= https://www.tapinto.net/towns/warren/sections/arts-and-entertainment/articles/raising-olympians-warrens-three-reed-siblings-c |title= Raising Olympians: Warren's Three Reed Siblings Competing In Sochi Olympics |last= Nemcek |first= Brenda A. |work= TAP into Warren |date=2014-02-06 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180108201631/https://www.tapinto.net/towns/warren/sections/arts-and-entertainment/articles/raising-olympians-warrens-three-reed-siblings-c |archivedate=2018-01-08 }}</ref>。她在三岁时开始练习花样滑冰，起初主攻单人滑，后来因为希望能够跳舞而开始改练冰舞<ref name=ST091008>{{cite news |url= http://www.skatetoday.com/2009/10/08/reed-joins-japaridze-to-compete-for-georgia/ |title= Reed Joins Japaridze to Compete for Georgia |first= Barry |last= Mittan |work= Skate Today |date=2009-10-08 |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928074655/http://www.skatetoday.com/2009/10/08/reed-joins-japaridze-to-compete-for-georgia/ |archivedate=2011-09-28 }}</ref>。

